    "content": "# 006: Organizational Messages\n\n## Overview\n\n\n\n## Reference\n\n* https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-365/admin/misc/organizational-messages-microsoft-365?view=o365-worldwide#setting-tenant-policies\n"
